AD_PROCESS_PARA.NAME: Period
AD_PROCESS_PARA.HELP: The Period indicates an exclusive range of dates for a calendar.
AD_PROCESS_PARA.DEFAULTVALUE: @SQL=SELECT P.C_PERIOD_ID AS DEFAULTVALUE FROM C_PERIOD P WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM C_PERIODCONTROL PC WHERE P.C_PERIOD_ID=PC.C_PERIOD_ID AND UPPER(PC.PERIODSTATUS)='O') AND EXISTS(SELECT * FROM C_CALENDAR C, C_YEAR Y WHERE Y.C_CALENDAR_ID=C.C_CALENDAR_ID AND P.C_YEAR_ID=Y.C_YEAR_ID AND AD_ISORGINCLUDED(@AD_ORG_ID@, C.AD_ORG_ID, @AD_CLIENT_ID@)<> -1) AND P.AD_CLIENT_ID=@AD_CLIENT_ID@ AND NOW() BETWEEN STARTDATE AND ENDDATE
